{"title":"图书分配","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":62,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-1686","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>图书馆按顺序排列有<span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">N</span><span style=\"\">本书需要维护，每本书的总页数不相同。现有</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">M</span><span style=\"\">位员工。可以给每个员工分配连续的一段书籍，让他进行维护。现在的问题是，怎么样分配，工作任务最重（需要维护的页数最多）的人维护的页数尽量少。 </span></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>第一行两个数，<span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">N</span><span style=\"\">、</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">M</span><span style=\"\">。接下来</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">N</span><span style=\"\">行，每行一个整数，表示一本书的页数。</span></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p class=\"p0\">任务最重的人最少需要维护的页数。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>5 3</p>\n<p>3</p>\n<p>2</p>\n<p>4</p>\n<p>1</p>\n<p>5</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>5</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>数据范围：<span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">N&lt;=10</span>5，<span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">M&lt;=N</span><span style=\"\">。一本书的页数最多</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">10</span>4。时间限制为<span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">1s</span><span style=\"\">。</span></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}